<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3219450">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Wed, 02/06/2013 - 08:54 | <a href="/news/2013-02-05/brace-stock-market-accident#comment-3219450" class="active">3219450</a></span>
